            <p style="color: #555; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.6;">
                This course is designed to help Study Group Leaders integrate AI tools into every phase of their BOLLI course lifecycle. 
                The structure begins with foundational online learning, progresses through practical application during active teaching, 
                and culminates in an intensive in-person workshop where SGLs bring real experiences to share and refine their skills.
            </p>
