                <ul class="objectives-list">
                    <li>Understand how generative AI works and why grounding it in authoritative sources through Retrieval Augmented Generation (RAG) is essential for credible course development</li>
                    <li>Master effective prompting techniques for different AI tools (Claude, ChatGPT, Gemini)</li>
                    <li>Use AI to research topics and generate course outlines</li>
                    <li>Create reading guides and discussion questions with AI assistance</li>
                    <li>Develop curriculum materials efficiently for 5-week and 10-week courses</li>
                    <li>Navigate basic technical skills: browser management, document uploads, switching between tools</li>
